highlights.text: “Tum Chhupa Na Sakogi - Unplugged” by Prashant Katheriya is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Lucknow, up 80 spots at #15.
Arijit Singh has the most spots on Top Songs Lucknow. “Jhoome Jo Pathaan” is the highest at #4.
“Maan Meri Jaan” by King has been on Top Songs Lucknow the longest, at 13 weeks straight.
“Tere Pyaar Mein” by Pritam, Arijit Singh, Amitabh Bhattacharya, and Nikhita Gandhi is the highest new entry on Top Songs Lucknow at #25.
